import React from 'react';
import { Card, Image, Button } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const CartComponent = (props) => (
    <Card>
        <Card.Content>
        <Image floated='left' size='mini' src={props.image}/>
        <Card.Header>{props.title}</Card.Header>
        <Card.Meta>200 Ñ€.
        <Button size='mini' attached='left' color='red' floated='right'>x</Button>
        </Card.Meta>
        
        </Card.Content>
    </Card>
    )

export default CartComponent;
